  "description": "This game in the <i>Crash Bandicoot</i> series features Crash and his cohorts participating in games a la the Nintendo game <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Mario+Party+series\">Mario Party</a>.<br><br>There are 7 minigame types, 4 of which are available from the start of the game. Each of the minigame types has 4 variations, for a total of 28 different minigames.  The minigame types range from bumper-cars to four-way pong.  The goal of every game is for the player to either score more points than their opponents or destroy them. Every minigame can be played with up to 4 players total, with AI sitting in for any unused slots.",
